caption:
🌟 How a Microsoft Engineer is Shaping Bihar’s Future with Lessons from Kota!

Born in Khagaria, Vatsalya Chauhan is the son of a welder

In his first try, he couldn't secure the rank he expected
But ALLEN Kota, offered him free coaching and lodging for next attempt

🌟 With a 382 rank, he was accepted into IIT Kharagpur this time
He secured a job offer from Microsoft

👉For most, this would be the end of a long drawn struggle 
But... this is not so for this young engineer

📍Inspired by Kota, this Microsoft Engineer decided to give Bihar the Kota transformation
He is setting up school for kids of Maoists in Bihar

❤️ Celebrating engineers who bring real change to the world

Happy Engineer's Day

#EngineersDay #ALLEN
